Package: wickrascreener
Type: Package
Title: Data-Driven Multi-Symbol Scan Core
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-screener over its C ABI hub: build a Screener
    from a spec JSON, drive it with command JSON and read back scan reports - the
    same protocol as the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-screener
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-screener/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-screener C ABI shared library (WKSCREEN_LIB) and
    its header (WKSCREEN_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
